reviewText:
I watched this once in high school, and always thought about getting it for myself, for those days when I just want to watch something violent and awful and funny. If you like WorldStarHipHop videos, theYNC(dot)com, Liveleak, and old-school rap/hip-hop, then this is for you.

Not for the faint of heart. If you've been looking for it, this is one of the only places that have it. If you've never heard of it, move along, unless you like to watch street fights, cars being damaged by the amount of hydraulics uses, or actual suicides/executionsall to the score of Dr. Dre and Ice Cube, among others.
